OL,3,CEx-Welsh Secretary denies trying to
OL,4,Cundermine devolution
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV Cymru Wales,
OL,7,Fthe former Welsh Secretary Simon Hart
OL,8,Fhas denied trying to undermine
OL,9,Fdevolution during his time as part of
OL,10,Fthe UK Government.
OL,12,FMr Hart was Secretary of State for
OL,13,FWales under Boris Johnson and
OL,14,Fsubsequently Chief Whip when Rishi
OL,15,FSunak became Prime Minister.
