OL,3,CEx-Welsh Secretary denies trying to
OL,4,Cundermine devolution
OL,6,FMr Hart repeatedly criticises Mark
OL,7,FDrakeford, who was First Minister at
OL,8,Fthe time, for what he claims was a
OL,9,F'politicised approach' to imposing
OL,10,Frestrictions.
OL,12,FHe writes about "the thankless
OL,13,Fchallenge of trying to work with a
OL,14,Fhighly politicised Labour Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment under Mark Drakeford, who
OL,16,Fwas determined to undermine the UK
OL,17,FConservative Government.
