OL,3,CEx-Welsh Secretary denies trying to
OL,4,Cundermine devolution
OL,6,F"His ambition was made much easier by
OL,7,Fthe nature of the devolution
OL,8,Fsettlement. In short, it grants
OL,9,Fdevolved government the power to spend
OL,10,Ftaxpayers' money with none of the
OL,11,Fresponsibilities.
OL,13,F"I was never a great fan of devolution
OL,14,Fin its current form (I voted against
OL,15,Fbut it went through on a paltry
OL,16,Fturnout in 1998) and my time in the
OL,17,FWales Office reinforced my scepticism."
