OL,3,CEx-Welsh Secretary denies trying to
OL,4,Cundermine devolution
OL,6,FIn the interview, he's asked by
OL,7,FPolitical Editor Adrian Masters if
OL,8,Fthat scepticism was behind decisions
OL,9,Fwhich placed new limits on the power
OL,10,Fof the Welsh Government.
OL,12,FHe says, "No ... listen, I voted
OL,13,Fagainst devolution in 1997, whenever
OL,14,Fit was, and I don't think I made any
OL,15,Fsecret of the fact that I think there
OL,16,Fare areas where you can make
OL,17,Fdevolution work, where localised
OL,18,Fdecision-making is to use the
OL,19,Fexpression, more effective than
OL,20,Fcentralised decision-making.
