OL,6,FIn one entry, at a time when things
OL,7,Fare looking bleak for the premiership
OL,8,Fof Boris Johnson, Mr Hart retells an
OL,9,Fexample of gallows humour shared with
OL,10,Fhis junior Wales Office minister,
OL,11,FDavid TC Davies.
OL,13,FHe writes that, "I have rehearsals for
OL,14,FWelsh Orals, so TC and I decide we
OL,15,Fshould announce the abolition of the
OL,16,FSenedd on the basis no one will notice
OL,17,Fand it might make us smile."
